task-1:
1. create a basic Html page structure with the doctype, html, head, meta, title and body tags 
2. the title will be "My Travel Blog"
3. Add comments to the code to explain each section, For example "this is the head section"
Task-2: 
1. create a heading tag that will have the text"My Travel Blog'
2. Format the text in your heading tag using italic 
task-3:
1. create a div and inside the div create a paragraph.
2. Add a button having the text "Read More"
task-4:
1. create a span tag which will be outside the div. it will have the text "What i bought"
2. format the text in your span tag bold.
3. create an ordered list of things you bought from the place you visited.
4. create another span tag with the text "My Favourite food" and make it bold. 
5. create an unordered list of your favourite food you ate in that place.
task-5:
1. insert an image of your favourite food using the img and add the src, alt, width, and height attributes to it.